The paper discusses the bias-variance tradeoff in neural networks, which is a topic commonly studied in the field of machine learning (cs.LG). The experiments and analysis conducted in the paper also involve deep reinforcement learning (cs.AI) and neural networks for computer vision tasks (cs.CV).
